alerts.description:
There is a risk of storm-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 75-90 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then north-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 105 km/h

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Height range: > 800 m; Max. gusts: ~ 60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west

There is a risk of light snowfall (Level 1 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: < 10 cm; in windward areas: < 25 cm

There is a risk of snowfall (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 800 m; Precipitation amounts: 10-20 cm; in windward areas: < 35 cm
